  "mainOuterHtml": "<main id=\"MainContent\" class=\"content-for-layout focus-none\" role=\"main\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n      <div id=\"shopify-section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW\" class=\"shopify-section\"><style data-shopify=\"\">\n  .article_content__wrpr {\n    padding-top: calc(16px / 2);\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  .article__hero-banner, .article__hero-banner img {\n    border-radius: 10px;\n  }\n  .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n    padding-top:  calc(16px / 2);\n    margin-left: 12px;\n    margin-right: 12px;\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  @media screen and (min-width: 787px) {\n    .article_content__wrpr {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n    .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<link href=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/t/18/assets/main-article.css?v=172269203489927186851771645050\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\">\n\n<div class=\"main-article__wrpr section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding color-scheme-1\">\n  <div class=\"article__hero-banner narrow-width\">\n    \n      <img src=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Rectangle_378_2654f331-9d68-4b84-9e05-fd4a339a770d.png?v=1770809454&amp;width=800\" alt=\"Experience Timeless Beauty, Every Day\" srcset=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Rectangle_378_2654f331-9d68-4b84-9e05-fd4a339a770d.png?v=1770809454&amp;width=352 352w, //dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Rectangle_378_2654f331-9d68-4b84-9e05-fd4a339a770d.png?v=1770809454&amp;width=800 800w\" width=\"800\" height=\"958\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"narrow-width\">\n    <div class=\"article_content__wrpr\">\n      \n        \n            \n            <span class=\"date\">07 Jan 2026</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            \n\n          \n      \n        \n            <span class=\"article_blog_title\">Blog</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 10px;\">\n              <h1 class=\"h3\">Experience Timeless Beauty, Every Day</h1>\n            </div>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\">\n              <p>True beauty isn't about chasing trends—it's about embracing what makes you feel confident and radiant at any age. At Ellara, we believe in skincare that honors your skin's natural wisdom while supporting it with the best nature and science have to offer.</p>\n\n<h2>Simple. Effective. Timeless.</h2>\n\n<p>Our philosophy is straightforward: quality ingredients, proven results, and rituals you'll actually look forward to. No complicated routines or empty promises—just products that work, day after day.</p>\n\n<h2>Your Skin, Your Story</h2>\n\n<p>Every face tells a story, and every skin type has unique needs. Whether you're in your twenties or your sixties, our collection is designed to meet you where you are and help you feel beautiful in your own skin.</p>\n\n<h2>Beauty That Lasts</h2>\n\n<p>Timeless beauty comes from consistency, self-care, and products you can trust. Start your journey with Ellara and discover skincare that grows with you—today, tomorrow, and every day after.</p>\n            </div>\n        \n      \n\n      <hr class=\"hr\">\n\n      <div class=\"article_page__social-icons align_ment--start\">\n        <button class=\"button article_page__social-share\" onclick=\"sharePage()\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\" width=\"144px\" height=\"144px\">\n            <path d=\"M 36.5 5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 30.236328 13.207031 L 30.121094 13.263672 L 16.738281 19.953125 L 16.623047 20.009766 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 17.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 30.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 16.626953 27.990234 L 16.738281 28.046875 L 30.121094 34.736328 L 30.23